<p>Race doesn't matter, ever. <br />Diety only use is for diety specific armor, many go Agnostic so they can access areas with illusion masks that you would otherwise be kos at. <br />The only stat that matters to a new bard is WISDOM, it is the ONE stat you will NEVER need.&nbsp;&nbsp;The rest do as you please, it's impossible to make a bad bard, how you play it is what makes or breaks you.  For more info, eqdiva.com.</p>
